Package: SCE
Title: Statistical Concepts Explorer
Version: 1.1.1
Authors@R: person("Psycholo.ge", email = "contact@psycholo.ge",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for learning statistics,
    game theory, data analysis, psychometrics, and machine learning.
    Features 65+ modules with guided explanations, interactive
    simulations, and quizzes.
